messages.message:
Hey team , i found a difference in the actual response and the documentation for the API
Get Conversation Information
The difference is in the documentation of the
*“documents”* key of the data.

Documentation
```{
  "id":1,
   "name":"name",
   "state":"state",
   "uploadTimestamp": "2024-01-15T09:30:00Z"
}```
While the actual response for a document element is only
```{
 "id":1,
 "name":"name"
}```
